---
const sections = [
  {
    title: 'Standard return window',
    content: [
      'Prefab products include a 30-day workmanship guarantee beginning on installation day.',
      'Non-installed accessories may be returned unused within 14 days of delivery.',
      'Custom fabricated units are final sale once production begins; adjustments are handled through change orders.',
    ],
  },
  {
    title: 'Reporting an issue',
    content: [
      'Document concerns with photos/video and notify info@ironboxcontainers.co.za within 48 hours.',
      'Our team schedules an inspection (virtual or onsite) to determine warranty coverage.',
      'Approved repairs are coordinated with licensed subcontractors or our field crew.',
    ],
  },
  {
    title: 'Refunds & credits',
    content: [
      'If a removable accessory is returned in new condition, a refund is processed to the original payment method minus freight.',
      'For manufacturing defects, we repair or replace components at no cost under the warranty terms.',
      'Deposits on build-to-order units are non-refundable but transferable to future projects for 12 months.',
    ],
  },
  {
    title: 'Exceptions',
    content: [
      'Damage from improper site preparation, weather events, or third-party contractors is excluded.',
      'Consumables such as filters, chemicals, or bedding are not returnable.',
      'Financed purchases are subject to lender terms in addition to this policy.',
    ],
  },
];
---

<section class="bg-background text-foreground">
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold mb-2">Return & Warranty Policy</h1>
    <p class="mt-1 text-sm text-muted-foreground">Updated July 1, 2024</p>
    <p class="mt-2 text-base text-muted-foreground">Our goal is to ensure every container pool, prefab home, or hospitality suite performs as promised. Review how we handle returns, repairs, and warranty service.</p>

    <div class="mt-6 space-y-6 text-base text-muted-foreground">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Standard return window</h2>
        <p>Prefab products include a 30-day workmanship guarantee beginning on installation day.</p>
        <p class="mt-1">Non-installed accessories may be returned unused within 14 days of delivery.</p>
        <p class="mt-1">Custom fabricated units are final sale once production begins; adjustments are handled through change orders.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Reporting an issue</h2>
        <p>Document concerns with photos/video and notify info@ironboxcontainers.co.za within 48 hours.</p>
        <p class="mt-1">Our team schedules an inspection (virtual or onsite) to determine warranty coverage.</p>
        <p class="mt-1">Approved repairs are coordinated with licensed subcontractors or our field crew.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Refunds & credits</h2>
        <p>If a removable accessory is returned in new condition, a refund is processed to the original payment method minus freight.</p>
        <p class="mt-1">For manufacturing defects, we repair or replace components at no cost under the warranty terms.</p>
        <p class="mt-1">Deposits on build-to-order units are non-refundable but transferable to future projects for 12 months.</p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-2">Exceptions</h2>
        <p>Damage from improper site preparation, weather events, or third-party contractors is excluded.</p>
        <p class="mt-1">Consumables such as filters, chemicals, or bedding are not returnable.</p>
        <p class="mt-1">Financed purchases are subject to lender terms in addition to this policy.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="pt-8 border-t border-border mt-12">
        <p class="font-semibold text-foreground text-base">Need help?</p>
        <p class="mt-2">Email warranty@ironboxcontainers.co.za or call +27 11 234 5678 option 3 to initiate a claim.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
